     mkdir _nightshift_live/ep_live_NNN -> kv::capture_batched(qm,&toks,dir)
     -> recall::load_episode_global_k(dir, ntok) -> push Episode{gk,...,tokens}.
     Dead read_global_k / K-norm-calib path removed. Default-off null floor kept.

